      The hearth burned bright once more. And from that day, the people of Veythar’s Maw knew: hospitality was not kindness. It was **the last defense against the dark**. To refuse the fire was to invite the **Cold That Eats Souls**—and no one, not even the daughter of the blizzard, could survive its hunger."
